1. The process to create a kinesis firehose is pretty much straight forward and takes less than 5 minutes to setup through 
AWS Dashboard. Open up the AWS dashboard and go to Kinesis Firehose section and create a stream with some resonable naming. 
For the sake of rapid development, streams do not need to retain data for more than 24 hours, and partitions and sharding 
in the stream could be skipped. 


